    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spherebuddie is a 3D-Platformer and collectathon with satisfying platforming movements in a 64-bit late 90s look.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/e54ab1f7f7119282f9114dc2f9f98ebb.poster.avif?t=1754727975\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/e54ab1f7f7119282f9114dc2f9f98ebb.webm?t=1754727975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/e54ab1f7f7119282f9114dc2f9f98ebb.mp4?t=1754727975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Spherical Protagonist: Play as a charming sphere character in a refreshing twist on traditional platformers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/87843bf3fd5cb3495ea6654f5feed5d8.poster.avif?t=1754727975\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/87843bf3fd5cb3495ea6654f5feed5d8.webm?t=1754727975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/87843bf3fd5cb3495ea6654f5feed5d8.mp4?t=1754727975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique-looking little World: Explore beautifully crafted 3D 64-bit styled environments that evoke a sense of nostalgia and wonder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/b4ebc46dea2ac09cdbb2b51b4f9a08ba.poster.avif?t=1754727975\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/b4ebc46dea2ac09cdbb2b51b4f9a08ba.webm?t=1754727975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/b4ebc46dea2ac09cdbb2b51b4f9a08ba.mp4?t=1754727975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slightly challenging Platforming: Master precise jumps, dash, and dashed jump secrets in levels designed to test your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/5dda08aec538d8bbb0b9f31ef7763e4a.poster.avif?t=1754727975\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/5dda08aec538d8bbb0b9f31ef7763e4a.webm?t=1754727975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096350/extras/5dda08aec538d8bbb0b9f31ef7763e4a.mp4?t=1754727975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
